title: AAA20 Group debuts cobot palletizer for food and protein processing
description:
AAA20 Group's CP-66-WD is a waterproof, IP69K-rated collaborative robot that can be power-washed like other production equipment.

The post AAA20 Group debuts cobot palletizer for food and protein processing appeared first on The Robot Report.
